data.description: Two story home featuring over 2,100 sq ft. includes 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, separate living room and family rooms and an open floor plan with large picture windows along the front. Beautiful upgraded kitchen and baths with granite tile counters and slate and tile floors. A large deck extends off the living and dining areas for entertaining and enjoying the views. Attached 2 car garage with work bench, RV parking, level green yard, in-ground sprinklers, nicely landscaped. All on 0.83 acres.
